Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.40,0:08:35.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開始亂來了 那個小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.93,0:08:41.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克洛德 快點過來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.93,0:08:43.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到這裡來 克洛德
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.22,0:08:47.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要磨磨蹭蹭的 我對你抱有很大的期望
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.44,0:08:50.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是刺耳的聲援
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.31,0:08:55.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,問題 請重複Yes Your Highness三遍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.57,0:09:00.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes Your Highness  Yes Your Highness  Yes Your Highness
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.64,0:09:06.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兒戲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.90,0:09:11.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說了Yes Your Highness
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.32,0:09:14.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看啊 他還是我的執事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.65,0:09:20.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是這樣地這樣地被克洛德愛著…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.07,0:09:23.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 您為什麼要哭
