Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.96,0:09:56.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天使死了？女王陛下也…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.26,0:10:00.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是怎麼回事 難道我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.30,0:10:04.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.37,0:10:13.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迷宮… 正在改變形態
